high_descs: Turn to the right, and go to the counter beside the sink.
Pick up the pan that is on the right side of the counter.
Take the pan and take a step to the left to the sink.
Place the pan in the sink, turn the water on and off. Pick up the pan from the sink.
Turn around to the left, and locate the toaster on the counter.
Place the pan on the counter between the stove and toaster.
anns.task_desc: Clean a pan and place it on the counter.

high_descs: Turn right and move to the counter past the stove.
Pick up the dirty pan on the counter.
Bring the pan to the sink on the left.
Clean the dirty pan in the sink with water.
Bring the cleaned pan to the counter right of the stove.
Put the cleaned pan on the counter right of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned pan on the counter, right of the stove.

high_descs: turn right, walk to the counter by the sink
grab the pan on the counter
walk to the left a little to the sink
put the pan in the sink, wash the pan with water, take the pan
turn around, walk to the counter by the stove
put the pan down on the counter
anns.task_desc: wash the pan from the counter by the sink, put the pan by the stove

high_descs: Turn to the right and go back to the sink.
Pick up the pan from the right side of the counter.
Take the pan and move a few steps left to the sink.
Place the pan in the sink. Turn on the water and turn it off. Take the pan out of the sink.
Carry the pan and move to the right, over to the toast.
Place the pan on the counter, to the left of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Clean a pan and place it on the counter.

high_descs: Turn and face the counter to the right of the sink.
Pick the pan up from the counter to the left of the sink.
Move to the left and face the sink.
Put the pan in the sink, turn on the water and then turn it off and pick up the pan from the sink.
Go to the right and face the sink to the left of the stove.
Put the pan down on the sink to the left of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean pan on the counter.

high_descs: Move to stand at the counter between the kitchen sink and stove.
Pick up the pan from the counter next to the stove.
Carry the pan to stand directly in front of the kitchen sink.
Place the pan in the sink, turn on the water, wash the pan, and remove it from the sink.
Carry the pan to the counter space to the right of the stove.
Place the pan on the counter between the stove and the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed pan on the counter by the toaster.
